Author notes
This map was made by Toxic! FTW!
xFire: RJOToxic

This is my very first map to ever make with Hammer editor. All the credit of this map goes to MooK, as he has helped me with everything from adding ammo to the guns, to simply putting a spawn point. He has helped me a ton and I appreciate it a lot. I would also like to thank Freakout, Pelican, WhaThe, G-Daddy, Puss'N'Boots, and everyone else who has helped contribute to the ideas for the map.

There are a few secrets, some better than others, but it is your job to find them. I have decompile-protected the map.

If you are wanting to create a new version of this map, please add me to your xfire, and have some maps present that you have done to show me you are worthy! :D

Enjoy!

-Toxic
